# Applesauce Fruit Cake

Christmas fruit cake!
  
## Ingredients

- 1/2 cup shortening with a little butter
- 2 cups sugar (1 white / 1 blown?)
- 1 egg beaten
- 1 1/2 cup applesauce
- 2 1/2 cup all purpose flour
- 1/2 tsp salt
- 1/2 tsp cinnamon
- 1/2 tsp allspice
- 1/4 tsp cloves
- 1/2 cup boiling water with 2 tsp baking soda mixed in (let sit)
### 1 and 1/2 cups of any kind of fruit filling example below
- 1/2 cup raisins and dates
- 1/2 cup nuts (walnuts)
- 1/2 cup canned fruit (mixed with flour)

## Instructions

1. Preheat oven to 350Â°F
2. In a large bowl, whisk together dry ingredients
3. Mix wet ingredients.
4. Add wet ingredients into dry ingredients and mix.
5. Bake in an angel food cake pan for 1 and 1/4 hours.
6. Enjoy!

### Enjoy!

